    "content": "All that was lost by the first Adam will be restored by the second. The prophet says, &ldquo;O Tower of the flock, the strong hold of the daughter of Zion, unto Thee shall it come, even the first dominion.&rdquo; And Paul points forward to the &ldquo;redemption of the purchased possession.&rdquo;",
