    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "God created the earth to be the abode of holy, happy beings. That purpose will be fulfilled when, renewed by the power of God and freed from sin and sorrow, it shall become the eternal home of the redeemed.<sup class=\"chapterendnote\"><a class=\"chapterendnote\">4<span class=\"chapterendnote\"><span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"RH 10-22-1908\" data-link=\"821.29386\">The Review and Herald, October 22, 1908</span>.</span></a></sup>",
