    "element_type": "p",
    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "<strong>Privileges of the Redeemed</strong>&mdash;Heaven is a good place. I long to be there and behold my lovely Jesus, who gave His life for me, and be changed into His glorious image. Oh, for language to express the glory of the bright world to come! I thirst for the living streams that make glad the city of our God.",
